data.description: Spacious and bright four bedroom home, located on a quiet and large culdesac which backs to greenbelt and the Carson River!  This property offers something for everybody.  Plenty of room to stretch your legs, garden, play, hike, relax, and entertain.  There is a separate living room area that can be used as a formal den or play area, along with a large great room off of the freshly remodeled kitchen.  Custom cabinetry and tile work, with stainless steel appliances welcome the chef in you. The centerpiece to the kitchen is a gorgeous island with a granite slab counter top, and unstoppable backyard and tree-line views of the river.  Cozy up by the gas log fireplace all winter long. Both bathrooms have double sinks, and all main living areas have new high quality LVP flooring.  Seller was planning to continue updating home, so most fixtures have also been updated.  Bring your own creative touch to finish up!!
